                ` + (typeof message !== 'undefined' ? message : 'Welcome to AmexingWeb') + `
            </h1>

            <p style="font-size: 1.25rem; color: #666; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                Secure, Fast, and PCI DSS Compliant E-Commerce Solution
            </p>

            <div style="margin: 3rem 0;">
                <a href="/api/status" class="btn" style="margin-right: 1rem;">Check API Status</a>
